---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AZVAI AI Playground | Vibecoding Portfolio"
  description="Modern vibecoding portfolio website for projects and AI training playground."
  current="home"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/assets/azvai_logo.png" alt="AZVAI logo" class="hero-logo" />
    <p class="eyebrow">ai.azvai.com</p>
    <h1>Vibecoding ideas shipped into real products.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Experiments, prototypes, and AI-native builds. A clean portfolio today,
      an automated training and dev platform next.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="hero-banner">
    <img src="/assets/azvai_circulos.png" alt="AZVAI circles" />
    <div class="hero-banner-text">
      <h2>Built fast. Validated in production.</h2>
      <p>
        Practical AI products, internal tooling, and data pipelines.
        Every project here went from idea to working system using vibecoding workflows.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Explore</h2>
    <div class="line"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="grid" aria-label="Portfolio sections">
    <article class="card span-6">
      <div class="card-icon">&#9881;</div>
      <h3>Projects</h3>
      <p>Index of all public vibecoding builds with architecture, stack, and implementation notes.</p>
      <p class="kicker"><a href="/projects">Browse projects &rarr;</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card span-6">
      <div class="card-icon">&#9889;</div>
      <h3>Training</h3>
      <p>Reserved area for API-driven automated content generation for AI training programs.</p>
      <p class="kicker"><a href="/training">Open training &rarr;</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card featured span-4">
      <h3>Design Language</h3>
      <p>Light base, #F1FFD2 accent, Inter typography, soft shadows, and rounded surfaces.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card span-4">
      <h3>Deployment</h3>
      <p>Astro for the frontend, GitHub for version control, Netlify for fast static deploys.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card span-4">
      <h3>Next Phase</h3>
      <p>Plug the team API into /training and automate pages, content routing, and generation pipelines.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
